---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import PrevNext from '../../components/PrevNext.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Multi-Generational Planning"
  description="It's in our DNA to provide for the next generation. Multi-generational planning documents your wishes and establishes plans so your children and grandchildren are cared for."
  eyebrow="Services"
  heroTitle="Multi-Generational Planning"
  heroSubtitle="Plan across generations — for what you pass down, how you pass it, and when."
  heroVideo="/videos/06.mp4"
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Multi-Generational Planning' }]}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split" style="margin-bottom:32px;">
        <div>
          <h2 class="underline">For Those Who Come Next</h2>
          <p style="font-size:1.15rem;">It's in our DNA to protect and provide for the next generation. Multi-generational planning helps you document your wishes and establish the structures that carry them out.</p>
          <p style="font-size:1.15rem;">So your children and grandchildren are provided for long-term — with clarity about what you've built and why it matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/multigen-dinner.jpg" alt="Grandfather and grandchildren at dinner — planning across generations" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(1,19,66,0.15);" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h2>What we plan for</h2>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li><strong>Education</strong> — 529 plans, custodial accounts, and direct tuition payments</li>
        <li><strong>Down payments and first homes</strong> — gifting strategies that don't burden the recipient with taxes</li>
        <li><strong>Inherited IRAs</strong> — SECURE Act rules, the 10-year distribution window, and how beneficiaries should plan</li>
        <li><strong>Generation-skipping strategies</strong> — trusts and exemption planning where appropriate</li>
        <li><strong>Family meetings</strong> — teaching the next generation how money works, and what you've built</li>
        <li><strong>Shared legacy decisions</strong> — charitable giving, business succession, real estate</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Beyond the money</h2>
      <p>The most durable family legacies aren't just financial — they're cultural. We help families articulate values, set expectations, and prepare heirs so that inheritance strengthens the next generation rather than derailing it.</p>

      <h2>Our fit in the process</h2>
      <p>We work alongside your estate attorney, CPA, and (where relevant) family-business advisors. We bring the investment and cash-flow modeling, the beneficiary coordination, and the long-term perspective that pulls the whole plan together.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <PrevNext section="services" />
</PageLayout>
